profile.bio: RepFix.com is a web based performance-based reputation management service that assists you maintain your online search reputation.   We're reforming the market by delivering the first completely performance-based work designed to aid you help your web results in Google.   In contrast with our competitors, we will not lock you into any agreements and we don't have a setup fee. And more importantly, we simply just charge a fee for the improvements that we achieve on your behalf!   We take great pride in ourselves on implementing the best performing techniques to promote you and your companies positive web based assets. This ensures that that prospective buyers as well as consumers find out the true nature of you or your small business .
